.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-list \- list BOLT-11 invoices from the node
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-list
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.RB [ --status
.IR pending | paid | expired ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Lists invoices from the CLN daemon via
.BR lightning-cli (1)
.BR listinvoices .
Returns a JSON array of objects:
.nf
[{
  "label": "...",
  "bolt11": "lnbc...",
  "amount_msat": <int>,
  "amount_sat": <int>,
  "status": "pending|paid|expired",
  "description": "...",
  "paid_at": <unix-ts|null>,
  "expires_at": <unix-ts>
}, ...]
.fi
.TP
.B --limit N
Return at most N invoices (default 50, max 500).
.TP
.B --status paid|pending|expired
Filter by status.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success (returns empty array if daemon unavailable).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-decode (1),
.BR lightning-account-recv (1)
